Fun fact: Our company is fully remote. That’s right, everyone at Toggl Plan works from a home office setup or from a coworking space. And it turns out, working from home is becoming more and more common.

Recent data from the U.S. Census Bureau revealed that in 2017, 5.2% of all U.S. employees worked from home. That’s a significant jump from the 3.3% reported in 2000. No wonder more homebuyers are including office space in their list of must-haves.off
